1 Sales Performance Analysis (Revenue, Profit, Quantity)
KPI: Total Revenue, Total Profit, Total Quantity Sold
Business Impact:
Measures overall business health and growth
Helps leadership evaluate market demand and sales efficiency
Used for quarterly targets and forecasting

2 Trend Analysis (Month-over-Month – MoM)
KPI: MoM Revenue Growth %, MoM Profit Growth %
Business Impact:
Identifies growth or decline patterns
Detects seasonality and performance shifts
Enables early corrective actions for declining months

3 Category & Sub-Category Performance

KPI: Revenue, Profit, Quantity by Category/Sub-Category
Business Impact:
Identifies top-performing and underperforming products
Supports inventory planning and product strategy
Helps focus marketing on high-margin categories

4 Geography Analysis (State-wise)
KPI: Revenue & Profit by State
Business Impact:
Highlights high-demand regions
Detects low-profit markets needing pricing or cost optimization
Assists in regional expansion decisions

5 Customer Insights
KPI: Top customers by Revenue & Profit
Business Impact:
Identifies high-value customers
Enables customer retention and loyalty programs
Helps in targeted promotions and upselling

6 Payment Mode Analysis
KPI: Revenue, Profit, Order Count by Payment Mode
Business Impact:
Understands customer payment preferences
Helps optimize payment infrastructure
Supports decisions on discounts and cashless adoption

7 Profitability Analysis (Margin Focus)
KPI: Profit Margin (%)
Business Impact:
Evaluates pricing effectiveness
Identifies high revenue–low profit products
Supports cost control and margin improvement strategies

8  Custom Insight: High Revenue – Low Profit Products
KPI: Revenue vs Profit Margin
Business Impact:
Flags margin leakage
Indicates need for pricing revision or supplier renegotiation
Improves overall profitability

9 Executive KPI Summary
KPI	Business Value
Total Revenue	Business scale & growth
Total Profit	Financial sustainability
Profit Margin	Operational efficiency
Quantity Sold	Demand strength
MoM Growth	Performance momentum
Category Leaders	Revenue drivers
Regional Leaders	Market opportunities
